interestingMethod

protected abstract boolean interestingMethod(org.eclipse.jdt.internal.compiler.ast.AbstractMethodDeclaration method)
Provided by a subclass to return true if this method should be processed. This is separate since some extra work is performed in order to call processMethod(org.eclipse.jdt.internal.compiler.ast.TypeDeclaration, org.eclipse.jdt.internal.compiler.ast.AbstractMethodDeclaration, java.lang.String).
